8
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:32,680
I...

9
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:34,480
I'm here to pawn some items.

10
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:45,040
You work hard every day but can't support yourself.

11
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:47,640
You can earn tens of thousands in Drunken Beauty.

12
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:51,000
I'm not that lucky.

13
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,640
You're the only one who bought my wine.

14
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:55,080
Mr. Fu, what are you doing here?

15
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,720
To rob you.

16
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,000
Hey, hey.

17
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:02,520
Mr. Fu.

18
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,480
Sir, sir.

19
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:04,120
Do you know each other?

20
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:04,880
We're

21
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,680
middle school classmates.

22
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,360
Which middle school?

23
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,160
You say.

24
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:14,960
Mujiu Li Trust School.

25
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:21,800
Ah.

26
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,320
Is this yours?

27
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,040
Yes.

28
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,920
This is Camy2750 imported from Switzerland

29
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,160
