32
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,640
Now it's equivalent to your ten years' salary.

33
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,920
Don't tell me it's your family's heirloom,

34
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:45,080
unless your grandparents were the Consul-General of Three Ports.

35
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,400
Mr. Fu is really

36
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,400
knowledgeable about the past and present.

37
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,760
You can't hide anything from you.

38
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,640
What's going on?

39
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,080
Tell me.

40
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,560
Tell me.

41
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,960
This is my grandmother's.

42
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,520
My mother told me

43
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,600
to leave this watch to my future daughter-in-law.

44
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,960
So, 3 years ago,

45
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,080
I gave it to her.

46
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,200
I never thought

47
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,160
