48
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,520
So...

49
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,840
So I admit,

50
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,080
I like her.

51
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,000
I know

52
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,200
