54
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,720
I just want to see her happy.

55
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,000
I'm happy.

56
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,040
I'm sorry.

57
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,400
You're so outstanding,

58
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:49,680
with both parents alive,

59
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,520
and a happy family.

60
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,120
I...

61
