I'm not good enough for you.

62
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,720
Yan, stop.

63
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,560
Mr. Fu,

64
00:02:58,920 --> 00:02:59,680
are you

65
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,520
