66
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,880
Why?

67
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,440
Thank you for your quick response.

68
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,360
No.

69
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:17,320
It's easier to say

70
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,760
