71
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,640
No.

72
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,280
You did well, too.

73
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,000
Jealousy

74
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,840
