81
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,320
Don't put trash in the car.

82
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:01,360
How's the cooperation with Mrs. Shi?

83
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,920
How's it going?

84
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,200
I've investigated Mrs. Shi's hobbies.

85
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,960
The file is in the back of the seat.

86
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:10,360
Mrs. Shi and her husband, General Manager Shi's Minghui Pavilion

87
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:11,520
is the largest agent of handicrafts and silk

88
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,480
in several countries in the south.

89
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,000
But in the past two years, she has begun to

90
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,760
