95
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,120
Let's go.

96
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,040
Hello, Mrs. Shi.

97
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,200
Mrs. Shi,

98
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,400
I've reserved the entire room today

99
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,000
