100
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,640
Quite the confidence, huh?

101
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:04,880
See you at the mahjong table.

102
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,520
Tell her

103
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,360
