104
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,320
I'll go.

105
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:29,960
It's fine.

106
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,920
It's been a while since I've played.

107
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,080
I'm itching to play.

108
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,040
Has Mr. Shi gone on a business trip?

109
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,640
