118
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,440
Come, sit down.

119
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,080
Why are you blushing?

120
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,280
Don't be shy.

121
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,000
Sit down.

122
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,160
Oh my.

123
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:23,480
He's not the same type as Jingjing.

124
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,560
Interesting.

125
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,480
Sit down.

126
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,280
Thanks for the invite, Boss Fu.

127
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,760
Feed me a tile.

128
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,880
I said, feed me a tile.

129
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,080
What are you thinking about?

130
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,520
Handsome guy,

131
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,640
