132
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,200
I've won!

133
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,360
Truly the Mahjong Champion of Aodao's Three Districts.

134
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,320
Impressive.

135
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,280
Let's go again.

136
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,000
Come on.

137
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,120
Mrs. Shi,

138
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,240
these mahjong tiles

139
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:53,520
