140
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,680
How do you like it?

141
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,360
It's jade?

142
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,640
I thought so.

143
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,600
Feels nice.

144
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,640
I brought a sample here

145
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,880
