152
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,920
and not comfortable to the touch.

153
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,800
So I went back and improved it.

154
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:29,920
Perfect.

155
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:30,800
My hands are small.

156
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,600
It's not easy to find a pair that fits me.

157
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:34,480
This pair is for you.

158
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,840
If you like it,

159
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,040
