169
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,400
Deal.

170
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,160
60,000.

171
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,280
Boss Fu,

172
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,640
