179
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,960
Can you win with the red dragon?

180
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,840
I win.

181
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,000
Thirteen Orphans.

182
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,160
Flower Tile as Wind Tile.

183
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,040
Pure to Mixed.

184
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,280
Double points.

185
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,680
Mr. Fu.

186
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,680
Your advisor is amazing.

187
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,400
Congratulations, Mr. Fu.

188
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:52,200
Eight points.

189
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,320
Narrow victory.

190
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,840
Sorry.

191
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:55,760
Mrs. Shi,

192
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,680
