210
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,440
Team One.

211
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,200
Ready to move.

212
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,040
Senior,

213
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,600
