216
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,960
When the time is right, give me the signal.

217
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,280
Then I'll go to save him.

218
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,480
People like him

219
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,920
