246
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:38,440
Tian Yan.

247
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:39,240
Be careful.

248
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,040
Are you okay?

249
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,960
Should we take her home first?

250
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:48,680
How can I let go of someone

251
00:16:49,400 --> 00:16:51,280
